### `review_patterns/escape-untrusted-fences.md` (new)

**Escape untrusted fences before injecting into prompts**

The same fence-escaping fix recurred across the sync and capture prompt builders. [confidence: likely]

```markdown
<!-- planwerk-review: captured from planwerk/planwerk-review#138 -->

# Review Pattern: Escape untrusted fences

**Review-Area**: security
**Severity**: WARNING

## What to check

Untrusted bodies injected into a fenced prompt block must have the closing delimiter escaped.

## Why it matters

A crafted body can close the fence early and smuggle instructions to the model.
```

